arStrings.szText: I've never met the man. I just know that Edgar fears him, and Edgar isn't afraid of anything.
She fears Osric, in particular she fears he will kill Edgar.
Osric led the group of Inquisitors who accompanied the Knights into Caldeum. He must have been someone important back up North...or had dirt on someone.
It's personal with Osric now. He can't stand the thought of one of his charges leaving the faith. He'll never let Edgar walk away.
